{"tid":1878473,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"夏寶龍上台，逃犯條例修訂有機會重新翻生，國歌法和國安法將被強制通過","createTime":"2020-02-13T15:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-07T12:25:24.000Z","uid":149978,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"41b753d4ca5e9f44270a4d99417b93a3a7588e36","tid":1878473,"uid":149978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"夏寶龍1952年12月出生，早年在天津官至常務副市長，2003年底與寧波書記黃興國對調，到浙江擔任省委副書記，後再升浙江省長，十八大後接替趙洪祝出任省委書記。<br />\n<br />\n他在2013年起力推「三改一拆」，即整改舊住宅區、舊廠區、城中村改造和拆除違法建築，其間摧毀逾2000間基督教堂的十字架以至整座建築物，又引發多宗流血衝突。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200213/s00001/1581569357031/%e5%a4%8f%e5%af%b6%e9%be%8d%e5%85%bc%e4%bb%bb%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e8%be%a6%e4%b8%bb%e4%bb%bb-%e6%9b%be%e4%bb%bb%e6%b5%99%e6%b1%9f%e7%9c%81%e5%a7%94%e6%9b%b8%e8%a8%98%e3%80%8c%e5%bc%b7%e6%8b%86%e5%8d%81%e5%ad%97%e6%9e%b6%e3%80%8d\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200213%2Fs00001%2F1581569357031%2F%25e5%25a4%258f%25e5%25af%25b6%25e9%25be%258d%25e5%2585%25bc%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25be%25b3%25e8%25be%25a6%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e4%25bb%25bb-%25e6%259b%25be%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e6%25b5%2599%25e6%25b1%259f%25e7%259c%2581%25e5%25a7%2594%25e6%259b%25b8%25e8%25a8%2598%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e6%258b%2586%25e5%258d%2581%25e5%25ad%2597%25e6%259e%25b6%25e3%2580%258d&d=3BA04jbrysekxL3Ytp5IvYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=0a53e868\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20200213%2Fs00001%2F1581569357031%2F%25e5%25a4%258f%25e5%25af%25b6%25e9%25be%258d%25e5%2585%25bc%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e6%25b8%25af%25e6%25be%25b3%25e8%25be%25a6%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e4%25bb%25bb-%25e6%259b%25be%25e4%25bb%25bb%25e6%25b5%2599%25e6%25b1%259f%25e7%259c%2581%25e5%25a7%2594%25e6%259b%25b8%25e8%25a8%2598%25e3%2580%258c%25e5%25bc%25b7%25e6%258b%2586%25e5%258d%2581%25e5%25ad%2597%25e6%259e%25b6%25e3%2580%258d&h=443eee86\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20200213/s00001/1581569357031/%e5%a4%8f%e5%af%b6%e9%be%8d%e5%85%bc%e4%bb%bb%e6%b8%af%e6%be%b3%e8%be%a6%e4%b8%bb%e4%bb%bb-%e6%9b%be%e4%bb%bb%e6%b5%99%e6%b1%9f%e7%9c%81%e5%a7%94%e6%9b%b8%e8%a8%98%e3%80%8c%e5%bc%b7%e6%8b%86%e5%8d%81%e5%ad%97%e6%9e%b6%e3%80%8d</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點解搵佢上台，佢上台代表左會咩？<br />\n佢<strong>曾推拆十字架，並成功鎮壓反抗者。</strong><br />\n<em>代表中國會命令香港在未來數年，強推一些不受香港人歡迎的法律，甚至惡法，然後強勢鎮壓，強勢通過。</em><br />\n<br />\n其實政府都講到好白了，呢些法律<strong>包括</strong>有：<br />\n1）<strong>國歌法</strong> （如無意外，8月前會通過）<br />\n2）國安法 / <strong>基本法23條</strong><br />\n3）中學及小學的<strong>國民教育科 / 愛國教育科</strong><br />\n4）<strong>重推逃犯條例修訂 </strong>/ 或與中國內地及澳門簽司法互助引渡協議<br />\n5）中港澳信貸記錄資料庫互通，<strong>並方便中國將香港人納入社會信用體系中</strong><br />\n6）中港澳刑事記錄資料庫互通，並方便中國將香港人納入社會信用體系中<br />\n7）繼續粵港澳大灣區計劃<br />\n8）<strong>網絡安全法</strong><br />\n9）版權條例修訂<strong>禁二次創作</strong>"},{"pid":"560b570014a3917602640209a73721a61787bb99","tid":1878473,"uid":127575,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:34:32.000Z","msg":"係就最好<br />\n<br />\n我要加快速度攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75dc438d3e5882e8d5ec7b5cdb435a2454c0df6","tid":1878473,"uid":103799,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"560b570014a3917602640209a73721a61787bb99","tid":1878473,"uid":127575,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:34:32.000Z","msg":"係就最好<br />\n<br />\n我要加快速度攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:43:26.000Z","msg":"攬炒??邊個炒??個政府輸左啲咩?"},{"pid":"16a1b39898cfdfeac1c3ff19914bc4de18911362","tid":1878473,"uid":25468,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T15:51:10.000Z","msg":"推個退休舊電池出黎 , 證明習種身邊根本無人 , 之前果件駱惠寧又係退休舊電池 , 開頭都係威係勢 , 一樣都係得個樣咩都唔敢做"},{"pid":"dd65347a9489ac5c7300450f27815537ea35e491","tid":1878473,"uid":149978